Link to the Soho Life app so you can use your voice to control your Soho Smart Home products. If you encounter any problems, please contact us at info@sohohome.com.au

CONTROL EXAMPLE:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your Soho PureHome Connect Smart Air Purifier with Voice Assistant after connecting Alexa to the product in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “Soho Life” app in Google Play or iOS App Store;
(2). Launch the “Soho Life” app and register a new account (or login if you’re already registered);
(3) .Turn on your Soho smart products and connect them with the “Soho Life” app. Please refer to your product manual for detailed instructions.
(4). IMPORTANT: You can rename your smart product with the “Soho Life” app. For instance, you can rename your SOHO SO-350WUI Smart Purifier as “My Purifier”. Once renamed, the product will be discovered as “My Purifier” in Step 9;
(5). Download the Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store. Launch the “Alexa” app and register a new account (or login if you’re already registered);
(6). Search the Alexa Skills directory for “Soho Life”;
(7). Click and Enable skill of “Soho Life”, then input your account username, password and region on the linking page;
(8).Talk to Alexa “Alexa, discover devices.” and wait till she says “Discover is completed”;
(9). Now all setup is finished. Try talk to Alexa to control your newly discovered smart product;

Air Purifier with Voice Assist:
“Alexa, turn on my purifier.”
“Alexa, turn off my purifier.”
“Alexa, set my purifier speed to low”
“Alexa, set my purifier to auto”
